{"tid":2076800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金正恩：暫緩對南韓採取軍事行動","createTime":"2020-06-23T22:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T03:26:24.000Z","uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1ebae6394b6256af0fc95bc0c07600461e445538","tid":2076800,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:47:15.000Z","msg":"金正恩主持會議　決定暫緩對南韓採取軍事行動計畫<br />\n<br />\n北韓勞動新聞報道，領袖金正恩主持勞動黨第七屆中央軍事委員會第五次會議預備會議，決定暫緩對南韓採取軍事行動計畫。報道表示，會議審視近期形勢，並決定暫緩人民軍總參謀部日前提出的對韓軍事行動計畫，會議又討論有關主要軍事政策的議案，以及反映旨在增強戰爭威懾力的對策的多份文件。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-24 05:37:35"},{"pid":"13ed4b281552d679075b0f87771ce1e13a524400","tid":2076800,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:48:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533754-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533754-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=b40c90be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533754-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=44a40643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533754-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6e7506d291204901c57db7988e33bea5549ca7d6","tid":2076800,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:49:56.000Z","msg":"走住屌"},{"pid":"3d60c9da282d28796535482127715e0799541a99","tid":2076800,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:50:48.000Z","msg":"威就佢妹拎<br />\n<br />\n低威就阿哥認"},{"pid":"bc7da753a16734424458fd2a96fffe845552bbcf","tid":2076800,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:52:06.000Z","msg":"返生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/